{"tid":235432,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港最近多左風化案，痴線佬一籮籮","createTime":"2017-05-09T04:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T15:02:31.000Z","uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d08d289497bf54ec127b342d17f45bde4f0bc0f","tid":235432,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"裸男暴走中大宿舍 跑入女宿房搞乜？<br />\n<br />\n沙田中文大學士林路，凌晨4時許，一名年約20歲男子，懷疑精神失常全身赤祼，在陳震夏女生宿舍樓層祼跑，警員接報趕至校舍，偕救護員合力將男子制服及披上毛氈，抬上救護車送院檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n警員事後到宿舍調查，4個多小時後，將另一名男子帶返警署調查。其後一名女子報稱感到身體不適，獲送院檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，警員調查期間，在宿舍撿獲少量毒品。案件暫列非禮及藏毒案處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170509&amp;guid=56669102&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170509%26guid%3D56669102%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1ded90b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170509%26guid%3D56669102%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=cf7d38ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170509&amp;guid=56669102&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"a3775437409d5bda397c88eabaabf934d97e101d","tid":235432,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"邊位手足"},{"pid":"03133021d706f8c02642270b65a1feb53822e880","tid":235432,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊位手足</blockquote><br />\n樓主男友"},{"pid":"b6facb9367c4c4862b0c7c4f0d366bfe5f685a1e","tid":235432,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊位手足</blockquote><br />\n樓主男友</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi